	dprr:hasNoteText "Liv. 2.21.1; Dion. Hal. 6.1.1-4; cf. 7.20.1; Chr. 354 (Atratino et Augurino), so also Fast. Hyd., and Chr. Pasc.; Cassiod. See Degrassi 88, 352f." .
